      "text": "Read by /dikw-gate at every firing to shape reviewer voice\nAlso read by /dikw-plan (ambition → task richness)\nAlso read by /dikw-report (strictness → CI-honest tone)\n\n🔒 Locked per session — can't change mid-run",
